    "body": "Running this enough times will eventually hang, as one task \"escapes\":\n\n```\nfn foo() {\n    task::yield();\n    task::spawn(foo);\n}\n\nfn main() {\n    let b = task::builder();\n    task::unsupervise(b);\n    task::run(b, foo);\n    for iter::repeat(1000) { task::yield(); }\n    fail;\n}\n```\n",
